<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="369" /> On <dateStruct value="--18" full="yes" authname="---18"><day type="name" full="yes">Monday</day>, <day reg="18" full="yes">18th inst.</day></dateStruct>, <persName n="Letitia,,Harriet,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00270" reg="default:Letitia,Harriet,,," authname="letitia,harriet"><foreName full="yes">Harriet</foreName> <surname full="yes">Letitia</surname></persName>, daughter of R. H. and <persName n="Pettis,,Mary,J.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00271" reg="default:Pettis,Mary,J.,," authname="pettis,mary,j."><foreName full="yes">Mary</foreName> <foreName full="yes">J.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Pettis</surname></persName>, aged <measure n="11months" type="date">11 months</measure> and <measure n="10days" type="date">10 days</measure>. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="370" /> The friends and acquaintances of the family are invited to attend her funeral from her father's residence, on <address><street n="3 Street">3d street</street></address>, this (<dateStruct full="yes"><day type="name" full="yes">Tuesday</day></dateStruct>) afternoon, at <time value="4oclock">4 o'clock</time>. </p> </div4> 
