<div3 type="orders" n="1" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head>Brigade headquarters.<lb /><placeName reg="Chafin's Farm">Chafin's Farm</placeName>, <date value="1862-08-18" authname="1862-08-18">Aug. 18, 1862.</date></head> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="456" /> Special Orders, <num value="270">No. 270</num>.--The <rs type="role" reg="Secretary of War">Secretary of War</rs> having ordered all officers and men who have been duly exchanged as prisoners of war to join their respective regiments and corps without delay, the officers and enlisted men, of the <orgName type="regiment" key="29VARegiment">29th Virginia regiment</orgName>, captured at <placeName reg="Rich Mountain, Randolph, West Virginia" key="tgn,2616904" authname="tgn,2616904">Rich Mountain</placeName>, and of the <num value="48" type="ordinal">48th</num> and <orgName type="regiment" key="59VARegiment">59th Virginia regiments</orgName>, captured at <placeName reg="Roanoke Island, Dare, North Carolina" key="tgn,7014345" authname="tgn,7014345">Roanoke Island</placeName>; all absentees without leave, and absent sick without proper surgeons certificates belonging to the above regiments, and all of the same who were not captured or paroled, and who have joined other regiments, will report at these headquarters immediately and without further orders. </p> <closer> By command of <signed><persName n="Wise,Brigadier-General,Henry,A.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00321" reg="default:Wise,Henry,A.,," authname="wise,henry,a."><roleName n="Brigadier-General" full="yes">Brig-Gen.</roleName> <foreName full="yes">Henry</foreName> <foreName full="yes">A.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Wise</surname></persName>.</signed> <lb /> au <num value="19">19</num>--10t <signed><persName n="Pearce,,James,H.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00322" reg="default:Pearce,James,H.,," authname="pearce,james,h."><foreName n="James" full="yes">Jas.</foreName> <foreName full="yes">H.</foreName>  <surname full="yes">Pearce</surname></persName>, A. A. <rs type="role">Gen.</rs></signed> </closer> </div3> 
